Package de.gmxhome.conrad.jpos.jpos_base.remoteorderdisplay

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RemoteOrderDisplayInterface
    Interface for methods that implement property setter and method calls for the RemoteOrderDisplay device category.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AreaBase
    Output request class for remote order display methods using row, column, height and width parameters to specify a video region.
    ClearVideo
    Output request executor for RemoteOrderDisplay method ClearVideo and base for method ClearVideoRegion.
    ClearVideoRegion
    Output request executor for RemoteOrderDisplay method ClearVideoRegion and base for method CopyVideoRegion.
    CopyVideoRegion
    Output request executor for RemoteOrderDisplay method CopyVideoRegion.
    DisplayData
    Output request executor for RemoteOrderDisplay method DisplayData.
    DrawBox
    Output request executor for RemoteOrderDisplay method DrawBox.
    Factory
    General part of Remote Order Display factory for JPOS devices using this framework.
    OutputRequest
    Output request class for remote order displays.
    PositionBase
    Output request class for remote order display methods using starting row and column parameters.
    RemoteOrderDisplayDataEvent
    Data event implementation for Remote Order Display devices.
    RemoteOrderDisplayInputErrorEvent
    Remote Order Display input error event class.
    RemoteOrderDisplayOutputCompleteEvent
    Remote Order Display output complete event class.
    RemoteOrderDisplayOutputErrorEvent
    Remote Order Display output error event class.
    RemoteOrderDisplayProperties
    Class containing the remote order display specific properties, their default values and default implementations of RemoteOrderDisplayInterface.
    RemoteOrderDisplayService
    RemoteOrderDisplay service implementation.
    RemoteOrderDisplayStatusUpdateEvent
    Status update event implementation for RemoteOrderDisplay devices.
    RestoreVideoRegion
